title: NFL ATL: Michael Sam's NFL future, salary cap casualties
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Michael Sam's NFL future, salary cap casualties
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- move from Studio 66 to the front office, analyzing which marquee NFL veterans could get the axe this offseason.  Elsewhere, the crew delves into all the biggest headlines from around the league, including NFL draft prospect Michael Sam’s announcement that he’s gay.  Don’t miss as the heroes get a surprise visit from Handsome Hank, who has a bone to pick over last week’s pod.  So, settle down, tune in and join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
